storyInfo: Following the Snowcap Incident, Sciurus and Yucatan go to Victoria to represent the Browntails, and attempt to make a deal with a local magnate to rejuvenate their clan.

attributes.content: Rus, are you done packing?
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Victoria's not like Kjerag. We're trying to work with the other side this time. Our standing's weak, and they WILL take advantage of that to tear us open.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: The only thing I can tell you is, there's no way of guessing what they're going to do exactly. It's up to you to determine.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Alright, alright, I get it! You're going to chew my ear off, ugh!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: If you have so little faith in me, why don't you do it yourself?!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Turn your brain on for once in your life and figure that out YOUR-self.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Why you...!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Alright, I've got no time to argue with you. Remember, this isn't an all-expenses-paid vacation. You're representing the Browntails.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Yucatan, keep an eye on your wife. Don't let her do anything stupid that would embarrass our clan.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Haha...
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Don't nod to that! Yucatan, whose side are you on?!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Don't get sidetracked.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Short version: pay more mind on this one. Eyes out, ears out, mouth shut. Don't shoot off like you did before.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: It's time you went out and broadened your horizons, anyway. Go and see the lands outside of Kjerag. See just what kind of place Victoria is.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Hmph...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Hey, you know... Ratatos.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: What?
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Is it me, or do you really wish you were going yourself?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Rus, over here.
attributes.name: Ratatos
Sciurus
attributes.content: Huh?

attributes.name: Sciurus
attributes.content: Hands to yourself, bitch! I don't have a temperature!
So why are you talking out of your ass?
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: I-I was just asking.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: If you had the chance back then... would you have wanted to visit Victoria, Ratatos?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Ah, I finally found you two!
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: Too many guests just now, swarming me, I tell you! Pardon me for leaving you in the lurch.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: Hardly, Mr. Harrison.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Thank you for inviting us. We've been having a delightful time.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Now, how nice of you!
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: I couldn't very well neglect you, not after you've come so far. Help yourself to any food or drink here, and if you need anything else, just fetch the closest servant.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: That's very kind.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Oh, do you need me to quickly demonstrate how to use all this cutlery?
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: ...We'll be fine.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Mr. Harrison, I think we should set that aside, and start discussing partnership arrangements between the Browntails and your own firm.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Ooh, very to-the-point, Madam Sciurus...
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: But I'm given to believe we've already reached firm consensus, haven't we, vis-a-vis partnership?
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: That is so.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: But I believe we still need to work out the details of a few terms.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Of course, you have no need to worry whatsoever.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: My assistant has the contract all ready. You can look over it whenever you have a moment to...
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: I've already read that contract.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Oh?
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: Let me be blunt. The Browntails cannot accept some of the terms within it.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Mm, hm...
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: So, your proposal, exactly?
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: We need to renegotiate the exact figures for provision of labor and revenue share.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Hmm.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: Yes, I will consider your concerns.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: So—
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Hold your beasties, now, Madam Sciurus.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: I'm of the mind that I've already been very generous with your cut on these orders.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: But...!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Now, not to worry, this is still the same win-win for us, and I have a very good impression of Kjelac myself. I would never have you or your family come out of this with losses.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: It's 'Kjerag,' not 'Kjelac,' Mr. Harrison.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Oh? Ah, of course, silly me, I always have trouble pronouncing that.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: You've visited Kjerag before?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: That... I can't say I have, but, quite some word of it has reached me in recent years.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: I've heard they roast entire meatbeasts at Kjelac dinner parties, the wine comes in big jars as tall as you or me, and they put on variety shows and the like too. I shan't for the life of me miss a chance to see it myself.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: You're joking.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Alright, I have to receive the other guests, now. Enjoy the party, my friends.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: W—Wait...! I haven't finished—
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Excuse me.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: (Mr. Harrison, there you are! Who are those two over there?)
attributes.name: Wealthy Woman

attributes.content: (Guests from Kjelac, wouldn't you know. They're from a fairly prestigious family in the area.)
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: (Ah, well, I've never heard of the place before...)
attributes.name: Wealthy Woman

attributes.content: (It's nothing more than some far-flung mountains. Not worth your concern, Dame.)
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: We're leaving, Yucatan!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Rus...
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Hrrrhhh...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Hffff... hrrrhhh...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Rus.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: We're alone now.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: (Deep breath)
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: AAAARRRGGHHHH HE PISSES ME OFF!!
attributes.name: Sciurus
Sciurus
attributes.content: HE PISSES ME OFF SO

attributes.name: Sciurus
attributes.content: HE PISSES ME OFF SO

attributes.name: Sciurus
attributes.content: MUCH!!
attributes.joined: Huh?Hands to yourself, bitch! I don't have a temperature!HE PISSES ME OFF SOHE PISSES ME OFF SOMUCH!!

attributes.content: THE HELL IS HIS PROBLEM?! WHO LET HIM ACT SO HIGH AND MIGHTY AT ME?! YOU THINK I CAN'T TELL HOW MUCH YOU LOOK DOWN ON US, HUH?! ON KJERAG?!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: HE WANTS TO TEACH ME HOW TO USE CUTLERY? EXCUSE ME? WHO CAN'T USE CUTLERY?! WHO PUTS A DUMB SHOW IN HIS DINNER PARTY? AND HE DOESN'T EVEN CARE TO SAY KJERAG RIGHT! IF WE WEREN'T GOING TO BE BUSINESS PARTNERS, ON KJERA-DAMNED-GANDR'S NAME, I WOULD PUNCH HIM INTO THE SUN!!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: I AM SO! SO!! SO!!! FURIOUS!!!!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: ...*sigh*.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Here, drink some water.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: No. My appetite is GONE.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Just drink some. Don't get those midnight stomach cramps.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: You can massage me then!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Fine, sure. I'll massage you.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Rus, you did well to hold out so long.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Hmph. What was I gonna do otherwise?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: If I went off right there, that bitch Ratatos would've jawed my head off later down the line.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: You did well.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: So where do we go from here?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Do you want to head back to the hall, or just go to bed for tonight?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Head back! Why wouldn't I head back?!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: All we got out of this was me, furious! We still haven't finished discussing the contract! Don't you dare think this is enough to make me back down!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Really? Are you okay?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Uh, duh, I'm fine. I'm doing just great.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: I didn't need Ratatos to tell me. I understand partnering here in Victoria is the Browntails' first step to contact with the outside world. I can't mess this up.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Not just that, I need every trick I up my sleeve to get us some good out of this.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: So it's fine. I can bear it.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Rus...
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Yucatan, you've seen everything I did the last two days—
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: I've never seen such big machines before. They look so clunky, but they run so smoothly.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: And there were nice even streets all the way here, and stations everywhere, and the sheer stuff in the shop windows makes my eyes spin.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: They don't even use candles for lighting this dinner party. It's electric lights...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Yucatan, Kjerag doesn't have any of this.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: And I think we SHOULD have all this.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: It just takes trains, pretty cities, stores in rainbow colors! All we've gotta do is build them!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: And then our kids can grow up around it all, and then when they're big, they can study abroad, they can go be tourists... wherever they want to go, they'll be able to.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Um, you said 'kids'...
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: N-No! I didn't mean THAT! W-What are you thinking?! I meant, um, you know, Kjerag's future children...!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Calm down, calm down, Rus, it's not on my mind, it hasn't been—
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: What? You've never thought about us having kids before?!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: I have... no, wait, not in that sense!
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Ahem.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Basically, we need to do more, for the future, before we can rest.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: That's what that stupid, horrible Enciodes thought as well, wasn't it?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: All that roundabout crap was a little too complicated for me, but the railroads and factories that dipshit built... Kjerag's changed a lot thanks to them.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Rus...
attributes.name: Yucatan
Sciurus
attributes.content: What are you laughing at...?

attributes.name: Sciurus
attributes.content: Q-Quit patting my head! You're gonna mess my hair up!
Here, Rus, hold still. I'll sort it out for you.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: I can't stand you... We're outside right now, you know!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Sorry, I couldn't stop myself.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: You're right. These are things we should have.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Things we will have.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Of course!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: But I never expected you to say it... or compliment Enciodes for once.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Ha, don't be stupid, Yucatan! I'd never say anything nice about the Silverashes!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: I'm just being realistic here. Enciodes might make me sick, but if this is what he's been seeing all this time, then I can slightly understand all the stuff he's been doing.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: I admit he's got a little skill, that's all. I'm magnanimous enough to say that.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: It's true. Enciodes has finesse.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Besides, I hate that stupid Gnosis guy by his side way more than I hate Enciodes!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: If it wasn't for that bastard pulling his pretend betrayal and scheming against us...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Under the circumstances, it was definitely a decent plan. Each side to their own, and none of the blame on him.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: I don't care! What are you defending him for, Yucatan?!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: I'm not...
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: (Glare)
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Alright, that was my bad.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: But it's been so long since it all blew over. When we make deals with the Silverashes in future, we're bound to run into their people again... When are you going to let go of your grudge, Rus?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: When death pries it from my cold, dead hands.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Ugh.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Look, it's apples to pears! I'm not going to wreck Ratatos's business, but don't count on me forgetting what they've done!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: ...*sigh*.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Not that the Matriarch seems to mind at all anymore.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: How, exactly?! That bitch might act like she doesn't care on the surface, but truth is? Her grudge runs deeper than mine!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Did you forget when we were kids and went out to play and we didn't call her along, and then Grandpa caught us when we came back and we had to write lines for a week?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: I'll still bet anything that was Ratatos's revenge! She DID that!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: You know we were playing outside for far too long, and that's why we were punished. We can't place the blame on the Matriarch.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Come on, you've got way too much faith in my sister!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: You know, though, speaking of...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Yucatan, have you ever gotten the feeling she kind of admires Enciodes?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Not like she's said it, but I can vaguely sense it.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Hmm... I agree, actually.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: If it wasn't for Enciodes's methods afterwards being too extreme, the Matriarch might not have reacted the way she did.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: You think so too? Say... you think the reason she put me onto this one was—so I could see all this?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Before we left, I asked her if she would've wanted to go to Victoria in those days too, if she had the chance.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Really... I know how she's been thinking.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Ratatos! Ratatos!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Ratatos! If you're there, answer me! I've been yelling forever! I bet you're just pretending you can't hear me again!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Why are you ignoring m... huh? What are you staring at?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Why shouldn't I ignore a little scumbag who doesn't even invite her sister?
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Who're you calling a scumbag?!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: A little runt who sneaks out to play all by herself and still wants me to cover for her, that's who.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: *cough* I'm... I'm sorry, that was my fault that time.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Next time I'll bring you! I'll get Yucatan to watch out for us!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Forget it, I'm busier than you anyway, and Grandpa's health is... whatever, who cares. Just don't stir up trouble for the next while, alright?
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Also, stop depending taking advantage of Yucatan. You're practically bullying him.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: How am I bullying him?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Because I said you are.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: So. What do you call me?
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Ratatos...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: The Firstborn! My elder sister!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: That's better, dear sister.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Hmph...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Hold on, are you trying to trick me again? Don't dodge the subject. What are you looking at?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Just some periodic intel reports, nothing special.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Grandpa lets you do this stuff already? He really trusts you...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Because I'm capable of handling it, unlike my darling little sister.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Why you...!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Fine, I'm not picking a fight with you.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: What kind of news is there this time? I mean, you've been staring at this forever...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Doesn't look like anything special...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Hm? The Silverash Firstborn's already left Kjerag?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: He went to study at Victoria... Wow, he's great at excuses. I bet he couldn't stand it in Kjerag any longer, so he just ran to somewhere else!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Is that what you think?
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: That's what everyone says. If we can stay, then who'd want to go somewhere they don't even speak the same language? I know I wouldn't.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: What? Ratatos... the Firstborn, what's with the funny look?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Stop. Put your hand away. I'm not at the point I need YOU to worry for me.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: You bitch... I was being nice!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Enough. Thanks for being nice, then.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: *sigh*...
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: It just fills me with something. It was all for the Silverashes' current situation, and him being able to push past his worries. That's what let him make a decision like this.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: What decision?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: The decision to abandon everything.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Enciodes... you really are a callous man.
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: That's what she said back then.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: I forgot all about it, but when I saw her and that stupid Enciodes in the fire... I don't know why, and it was so many years ago, but it just instantly came back to me.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: That's when it clicked. Ratatos wasn't occupied with any of the thoughts we thought she was.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Do you think... the Browntail clan has been a burden on her, this whole time?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Was this before the end of the Patriarch?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Yeah. Not long after that, Grandpa passed away.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: You know now that Grandpa's health was already shot by then. Ratatos just kept the wool over our eyes...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Too many people had eyes on the Browntails, and the Matriarch was still too young. Some people were bound to get ideas.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Yeah. It got so busy for her she didn't even sleep. She had the heaviest bags under her eyes and thought I'd just miss them... Her temper got awful too. Ragging on me all day.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Yucatan.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Back when I wasn't convinced, when I kept trying to disagree with Ratatos... I was being such a dumbass, wasn't I?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: No—
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Okay, stop, don't you say anything!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Mmph!
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: I know I was stupid then and I didn't help anything, but I sure ruined plenty! I was stupid to the max! It's fine, okay, I know all the way deep down!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: It's whatever from anyone else, but you're the only one who can't say it.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: You're not allowed to yell at me. I wouldn't be able to take it.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Rus... let me finish.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: You're brilliant. I've never once thought you were stupid.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Ugh, you... How do you say this stuff so straight?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Hmm? Do I?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: I don't think you're stupid, and neither does the Matriarch...
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: She totally does!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Alright... but she wouldn't fault you. You've always been trying to do a little something, and she's always trying to put faith in you. Haven't things turned out pretty great now?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: I know that, I'm just still a little... angry.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Angry at myself, and angry at Ratatos.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Why couldn't I realize sooner, and why does she have to love showing off so much?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Well... do you want some real talk?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: If it's not nice, don't say it.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Come on, that won't do.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Showing off probably runs in the Browntail family by now. You're not much different to her there, Rus.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: So, our reluctant bravery-lover Madam Sciurus, do you have a plan to persuade that Mr. Harrison, and knock his greed down a few pegs?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: I—
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Hold on... what noise is that?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: What a wretched dinner party.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: Am I to believe Mr. Harrison has the courage to purchase a noble's land, but not the bravery to receive me as a guest face-to-face?
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: You lot.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: Your orders.
attributes.name: Hostile Man

attributes.content: Give our Mr. Harrison a little gift.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: No cold feet to be had here. Teach this man how the mercantile should treat the aristocracy.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: On it!
attributes.name: Hostile Man

attributes.content: Argh!
attributes.name: Wealthy Woman

attributes.content: Q—Quickly, fetch Mr. Harrison!
attributes.name: Wealthy Woman

attributes.content: (What the hell? They're wrecking the whole hall.)
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: (Is that Victorian noble their leader? What is this meant to be...?)
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: (Looks like he and Mr. Harrison got into a mix-up.)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: (He's destroying the house. That can't be your average mix-up.)
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: (Want me to take a look?)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: (Hold on a bit longer. We can't just show up that casually. At least not right now!)
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: (But I think this might just be a good opportunity...)
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Viscount Evans!
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: W—We're honored to have you! Why didn't you send word in advance? I heard you were holidaying in Leithanien; I hardly thought...
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: Mr. Harrison, you're quite the well-informed one on the subject of my travels.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: You hardly thought I would return early. I imagine I've thrown a hardy spanner in your schemes, Mr. Harrison.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: Tha—Tha... What are you...
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: Now, Mr. Harrison, none of that silly countenance.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: You've been fraudulently snatching up shares in our joint firm, depressing prices and then purchasing the land on the sly while I was gone from the country. Not a good fit with your pathetic, wide-eyed look.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: Viscount Evans, is this really called for?!
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: Our partnership is still in effect! If it's a question of interests, we can still hash things out again... This is hardly how you treat your joint associate!
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: But of course I haven't forgotten our partnership.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: And yet still, I would dearly suffer for not letting off a little steam here.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: (A dispute of interests between this merchant and this noble...)
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: (Ratatos pushed me through a bunch of material before we left, so I knew about this, but who knew I'd see it first-hand.)
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: (But with this...)
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: (Do you have an idea, Rus?)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: (Yep. You just asked me if I had a plan for how to negotiate with Mr. Harrison.)
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: (Now I do—quick, Yucatan, here's our chance!)
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: You can't... You can't just do this!
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: Oh, can't I?
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: Mr. Harrison, let's be crystal-clear. Suppose I *do* do something to you! Then, they'll report that 'Pitiful Sir Harrison sadly passes away in duel with Viscount.'
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: Bahah, you can't possibly hope they'd lay hands on a noble?
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: (Sir.)
attributes.name: Hostile Man

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: (People got a lot of our guys knocked out now, only a few up still.)
attributes.name: Hostile Man

attributes.content: (And seems one of the guests called the police. Look...)
attributes.name: Hostile Man

attributes.content: You're not as dull as you suggest, Harrison. Fine job on finding some lackeys.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: What...?
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: Enough of the tomfoolery!
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: I'd come in thinking there would be future leeway for discussion if you were tactful enough here, but it seems you don't quite agree.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: Hmph. Today was just a lesson. We're far from through yet.
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: We're leaving!
attributes.name: Noble Man

attributes.content: They're just gone now?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Ugh... What about these guys, then?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: The red-haired Zalak carelessly dumps the people over her shoulder in front of the magnate.
Just put them here. Someone will deal with them.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Ah... are these all—Viscount Evans's...
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: You don't mean those 'lackeys' he mentioned were—
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: If you don't have anyone else to choose from, then I imagine you mean us.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Are you alright, Mr. Harrison?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: I escaped the worst of it, though I must seem an awful fool to the two of you, and, well, er...
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: No matter what, I thank you with all my soul.
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: Only, having set about to the Viscount's men like so, I worry in future, er... *sigh*...
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: Mr. Harrison.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Let me be straightforward about that—your partnership with that noble's in for a rocky ride, isn't it?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Well...
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: You've publicly offended him now we've beaten up his entourage, and it looks like he's a rung on the ladder above you, so you've got no way to get at him. Is he going to just keep working with you?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Based on what I know, your firm is in the key phase of its expansion right this moment, and if your partner pulls out midway, that'll be a massive blow to you, right?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Wh... What are you getting at here?
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: You can't be telling me you just did all that on purpose?!
attributes.name: Victorian Magnate

attributes.content: Come on, I'm doing nothing more than talking facts here, that's all. Don't go and overthink it.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: You're stuck between continuing to beg to that noble, or searching for a new associate under pressure. We have a small, little proposal there...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: We Browntails are one of Kjerag's Three Clans. A single puny Victorian noble poses no threat to us. If you're inclined, the Browntails will be your most reliable business associates.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: How about that, Mr. Harrison? Regarding that partnership between us—
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: —Is it me, or do you think we can renegotiate now?
attributes.name: Sciurus
